  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12"><img src="/media/13077393/ski-bundle-image-website.jpg" alt="Half price ski hire or carriage" data-udi="umb://media/6d8549dacfe54a2583684882295ffb58" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Ski 2020/21 is now on sale!<br /></strong>The wait is over, you can now book your 2020/21 ski holiday. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Take advantage of our <strong>fantastic early booking offer</strong> and check out <strong>what's new for Winter 2020/21.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Half price ski hire or carriage - when you book your lift pass with us (save up to £129 per person) - T&amp;C's apply.</strong></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g12">
<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>What's New for Ski 2020/21<br /><br /><br /></strong></h1>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">Half Price Ski Hire or Carriage</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays"><img src="/media/13077378/les-brevieres-exterior-2.jpg" alt="Half Price SKi Hire or Carriage" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">We're rewarding our early bookings with <a data-udi="umb://document/3566891a2b9142d4afe57ea30f084428" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3566891a2b9142d4afe57ea30f084428}" title="Ski Hire Offer"><strong>'half price ski hire or carriage'</strong></a> when you book your lift pass with us for winter 20/21. Save up to £129 per person, offer is available while stocks last. T&amp;C's apply.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">Group Discounts</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays"><img src="/media/13077378/les-brevieres-exterior-2.jpg" alt="Free lift passes for children" data-udi="umb://media/e62aeb38256141be8ebad68eeb8da8a9" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">We're rewarding our <a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">groups</a> with some great discounts. Give our reservations team a call with your group size and preferred destination and they can tell you how much you can save in winter 20/21!</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a name="backtotop"></a><a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets">Ski Total from Inghams</a><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra"><br /></a></h3>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets"><img src="/media/13081487/fra_val_larocheure_ext_p17.jpg" alt=" alt=" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Looking for an authentic chalet experience? We're proud to offer new properties run by our sister company <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.skitotal.com/" target="_blank">Ski Total</a>. Ranging from a cosy 6 person <a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets">chalets</a> up to 70 person <a data-udi="umb://document/7bfe7675d92e4c888cf5dee0c78eb888" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bfe7675d92e4c888cf5dee0c78eb888}" title="Chalet Hotel">Chalet Hotels</a> across France, Austria and Italy.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b9da978fccc34f6fbc7c87d94c360842" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b9da978fccc34f6fbc7c87d94c360842}" title="Half Price lift Passes - Winter 2020/21 - T&amp;C's"><strong style="font-size: small;">Half Price Ski Hire or Carriage Offer - Terms and Conditions </strong></a></p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
